A Series of Bayesian Fish Growth Models

Alexandra Norelli

2024-09-02

Clean and Examine White Perch Otolith Data

Histograms and Scatterplots

JAGS Models

These chunks create and run 3 JAGS models, one with just the measured length at ages, one with all the length at ages, and a third with a subset of ages 1-5. Loosely based off Ortiz de Zrate and Babcock (2016).
